{"tid":1764187,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡正元給王立強的公開信","createTime":"2019-12-01T02:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T02:54:27.000Z","uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6eafb41a861c6f5002b71d9a962225440b6c8cbf","tid":1764187,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T02:33:51.000Z","msg":"王立強兄<br />\n妳的風光時刻已經落幕了<br />\n妳在2011年考進<br />\n安徽財經大學的<br />\n「文學與藝術傳媒學院」<br />\n的「繪畫系」<br />\n這所財經大學有很多財經界人士<br />\n所以不難打聽妳的背景<br />\n雖然妳念的是合並而來的科系<br />\n妳在學校也不出色<br />\n但妳在澳洲短暫的「間諜生涯」<br />\n已經成為校內的大名人<br />\n讓妳的系主任周路<br />\n突然想起有妳這個學生<br />\n每個老師學生提到妳<br />\n無不嘖嘖稱奇<br />\n妳竟然有本事騙倒<br />\n「澳洲周玉蔻」Nick McKenzie<br />\n讓他替妳搞了60分鐘影片<br />\n連美國AIT也影射地放入臉書<br />\n美國紐約時報也快速轉載<br />\n還有臺灣的蔡英文也以妳為傲<br />\n大張旗鼓地查辦妳的「假上司」<br />\n2015年妳快畢業時<br />\n初試啼聲騙一個<br />\n想考上妳的母校的學生家長<br />\n2016年妳被輕微判刑<br />\n證明妳的詐騙專業<br />\n比妳的繪畫專業更行<br />\n2017年妳娶方人玉<br />\n陪妳們去蚌埠龍子湖<br />\n辦結婚登記的同學好友<br />\n現正拿著妳們的結婚照<br />\n四處渲染<br />\n2019年2月妳在上海騙了<br />\n人民幣460萬元<br />\n也以妳的美術專長<br />\n制作妳夫妻倆的假證件<br />\n於2019年4月趕快跑去香港<br />\n令人好奇的是<br />\n妳在香港有沒有從台灣方面<br />\n的人員再騙一筆錢跑去澳洲<br />\n2019年6月妳即向澳洲<br />\n申請政治庇護<br />\n9月就把「澳洲周玉蔻」<br />\n唬的一楞一楞<br />\n或許應該說<br />\n是不是台灣方面有人給了錢<br />\n讓妳們合作無間<br />\n11月份就在美國CIA協助下<br />\n演出一出「中國間諜鬧劇」<br />\n其實不管這出鬧劇<br />\n如何收尾<br />\n妳應該已有很豐厚的酬勞<br />\n這筆酬勞不管是誰給的<br />\n數字應該都不小<br />\n有趣的是<br />\n妳在學校時的同學好友<br />\n都希望妳繼續行騙天下<br />\n尤其是騙台灣人和騙白人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pbWW8sy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpbWW8sy.jpg&h=c90da4cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a9f31ea39f7edaf134b8560db13c9229c938132","tid":1764187,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T02:35:02.000Z","msg":"又抹黑"},{"pid":"50e70b85386025d140cfb12ea51b1ef2a6a1dc98","tid":1764187,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T02:38:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.skynews.com.au/details/_6110322131001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.skynews.com.au%2Fdetails%2F_6110322131001&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BxQ2JDI1%2B2PXXyGzAukhOpM%3D&h=36ad8b73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.skynews.com.au/details/_6110322131001</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ij5kOPpglVw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIj5kOPpglVw&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BxQ2JDI1%2B2PXXyGzAukhOpM%3D&h=3c3ad73e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ij5kOPpglVw</a>"},{"pid":"e6ba4c2d108394337c67cfabc9c50fb9030c31c7","tid":1764187,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T02:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sMsjmQG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsMsjmQG.jpg&h=bad65f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gQJbcXj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgQJbcXj.jpg&h=082fefc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fpWzVaC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfpWzVaC.jpg&h=973b13d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"811a475c7b2d6c0e45d3c6ba369e1852d5f48f43","tid":1764187,"uid":264709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T02:48:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\">也以妳的美術專長<br />\n制作妳夫妻倆的假證件</span><br />\n無雙郭富城咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d18c871312f8be8540594ccfd7c2085515650a","tid":1764187,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T02:51:26.000Z","msg":"條友真係弱智㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d633a27bd58413a2212c7cbe1557339917c364","tid":1764187,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T02:54:27.000Z","msg":"國民黨